Package base_SOM_Objects.som_examples

Class SOM_ExampleManager

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.SOM_ExampleManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
SOM_GeomExampleManager
public abstract class SOM_ExampleManager extends Object
this class will manage data handling for all examples of a particular type. Instances of this class are owned by a map manager;
Author:
john

      constructor for SOM example manager
      Parameters:
      _mapMgr - owning map manager
      _exName - descriptive name of data this example manager is handling
      _longExampleName - longer name
      _flagVals - array of flag vals : idx 0 : if should validate or not, idx 1 : if bmus should be saved via single thread or multi-thread mechanism
